Felwithe has an interesting mix of player charactes that come through there.  it's about 1/3 greedy newbie scavenger beggars who don't care that I'm killing their guards but beg me to let them loot, 1/3 people who don't care who buff my pet (usually low lvl buffs, but hey, the thought that counts, right?) and wish me luck, and 1/3 role player high elves who tell me how evil I am and stuff like that, which I actually enjoy.  not to mention I meet a lot of newbies and low level mages who have questions I am happy to answer.  have even had a few new mages send me tells to say they made a mage after watching me mow down their guards, heh.<br>
