Just after the patch that put the froggys in to Grobb For the honour of my first character and for the fact I like me 2 troll alts I decided to start Killing Froggys.<br>
<br>
All I could say was WOW there was 40 peps in Grobb all killing the frogs like there was no tomorrow.<br>
